Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Michael Deaver case
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xq2k
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 May 1986
US ethics committee to investigate allegations of improper lobbying by former White House aide Michael Deaver. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less